snippet.title: New Super Lucky's Tale Trailer #2 – "Meet Lucky!"
snippet.description:
Leap into adventure! #NewSuperLuckysTale is launching worldwide on Nintendo Switch this November 8, 2019. Join Lucky on his quest to rescue the Book of Ages from the mysterious Jinx and his Kitty Litter underlings in this 3D platforming adventure for all ages and skill levels.

Pre-order your copy today! https://playfulstudios.com/new-super-luckys-tale/


Follow Lucky on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playfullucky
Heart Lucky on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playfullucky/
Friend Lucky on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayfulLucky/
